body.p:
In case you need to add some of the map metadata to the header of the front page, in this example the
                creation date, in your customization css add
            the following CSS
                rules:front-page > *[class ~= "map/topicmeta"] > *[class ~= "topic/critdates"] > *[class ~= "topic/created"]{
    string-set: mapcreated attr(date);
}


@page front-page {    	
     @top-center {
          content: "Created: " string(mapcreated);
     }
}The
                    front-page is the name of a page that used to present the
                    oxygen:front-page element. The above page rule is combined with the default
                styles.
